    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this absolute gem. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's completely spotless inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one. Come by and see for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
