    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in absolute showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a deep, mirror-like exterior finish completely free of stone chips, swirls, or blemishes. The interior is equally breathtaking, featuring pristine leather upholstery with no bolster wear and that unmistakable factory-fresh scent. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates with precision, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history and remarkably low mileage. This is a true collector-grade example that drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this vehicle stands in a class of its own.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
